al/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為左目的幾多年都肯學既 其實唔需要問"},{"pid":"c2777e8dd746a1f6c83a80c3c7ccaa819eacf2dc","tid":2045433,"uid":391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T23:04:06.000Z","msg":"咁要睇係咩小說 同你一日用幾多時間學/溫<br />\n如果有人guide住你學同練 而你一日可以用至少5-6個鐘去讀嘅，可能半年至1年已經可以睇得明簡單嘅<br />\n難嘅例如文學作品可能要多1年左右 當然最後都要睇你資質同學習方法 <br />\n最緊要睇多啲聽多啲"},{"pid":"8dd7fe0bba58d0c593056f1870b74e1683b59c79","tid":2045433,"uid":69650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T00:26:45.000Z","msg":"學左句子結構之後<br />\n你識拆開句野黎查字典可以好快<br />\n唔查字典要半年（全日制）"},{"pid":"8525959524ee360afe4e1f44134478a2a1d00832","tid":2045433,"uid":136414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T20:24:44.000Z","msg":"一個月之後終於背到50音（好似係）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31c90a1600ced22c11773b57c9450f9c658278b","tid":2045433,"uid":145928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T20:55:31.000Z","msg":"你從0成點先?平時做咩嘅先?"},{"pid":"42675c5fb5a2ad64b1976d45190c8f04c5e8eed5","tid":2045433,"uid":9736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8525959524ee360afe4e1f44134478a2a1d00832","tid":2045433,"uid":136414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T20:24:44.000Z","msg":"一個月之後終於背到50音（好似係）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T21:06:24.000Z","msg":"咪撚玩啦伍寶 俾錢搵人譯好過啦"}]}